and Telegram sessions that have spun up in the meantime.\\n\\nLooking at the timestamp comparison, the baseline was recorded at 18:26 UTC and we're now at 19:28 UTC—one hour has passed. The three monitored cron jobs and the Telegram group session all show updated activity since then, with no state changes or failures detected.\\n\\nThe pipeline is still healthy with the MCPs functioning normally, and the DTLX report sent successfully at 18:26 UTC based on the message history. This is a stable state—silent exit.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Comparing current state (19:28 UTC) vs. stored baseline (18:26 UTC):\\n\\n| Session | Baseline | Current | Δ |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| cron:ed2d0b5d | ✅ running | ✅ running (updated 19:24 UTC) | — |\\n| cron:6f3323ef | ✅ running | ✅ running (updated 19:28 UTC) | — |\\n| cron:e7885813 | ✅ running | ✅ running (updated 19:19 UTC) | — |\\n| telegram:group:-5163901258 | ✅ running | ✅ running (updated 19:03 UTC) | — |\\n\\nNo state transitions. No new failures. No blockers. Pipeline stable. **Silent exit.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 29209,\n            \"output\": 536,\n            \"totalTokens\": 44107,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 418,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776194985079,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dc8aaaa0830ed0cd8416da2485e4f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"37a93f23\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"